SVN

Users

+ Heroes now level up and learn new skills based on race tables from HoMM II
  (afletdinov)

Developers

+ Army::Troops has been split into Army::Troop (for storing monster type, total
  number, and primary skill) and Army::BattleTroop, which holds information
  about animation, hit points, and position. (revvy)
+ Renamed uses of HighestTroop to FastestTroop (revvy)
+ Introduced army_types.h, spell_types.h, and audio_interface.h for inclusion
  by headers to reduce uneeded dependencies. (revvy)
+ Moved all SDL dependencies out of header files to reduce build times. (revvy)
